      "source": [
        "import networkx as nx\n",
        "from node2vec import Node2Vec\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "from matplotlib import pyplot as plt\n",
        "#from sklearn.datasets.samples_generator import make_blobs\n",
        "from sklearn.cluster import KMeans\n",
        "from random import randint\n",
        "from sklearn.manifold import TSNE"
      ],
      "execution_count": 0,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "USPuxqPpDafa",
        "colab_type": "code",
        "outputId": "07d3e548-b925-4e49-d988-cdda5b0f5365",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 35
        }
      },
      "source": [
        "from google.colab import drive\n",
        "drive.mount('/content/drive')"
      ],
      "execution_count": 11,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Drive already mounted at /content/drive; to attempt to forcibly remount, call drive.mount(\"/content/drive\", force_remount=True).\n"
          ],
          "name": "stdout"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "8RDwBcohDoay",
        "colab_type": "code",
        "colab": {}
      },
      "source": [
        "G = nx.read_edgelist('/content/drive/My Drive/data/AuthorCollaboration.txt', delimiter=\"\\t\", create_using = nx.Graph(),nodetype = str)\n",
        "\n",
        "df = pd.read_csv('/content/drive/My Drive/data/HEPcommunity.csv', usecols=['Node', 'Community'])\n",
        "df.columns = list(map(str.lower, df.columns))\n",
        "a = df['community']"
      ],
      "execution_count": 0,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "d5yus8sQFEKM",
        "colab_type": "code",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 35
        },
        "outputId": "38e511f4-ce85-49f4-c595-b9ecd7a57b3a"
      },
      "source": [
        "node2vec = Node2Vec(G, dimensions=20, walk_length=16, num_walks=100, workers=2)\n",
        "\n",
        "fix_formatted_positions = lambda x: x.split('_')[0] if x in G else x\n",
        "reformatted_walks = [list(map(fix_formatted_positions, walk)) for walk in node2vec.walks]\n",
        "node2vec.walks = reformatted_walks\n",
        "\n",
        "model = node2vec.fit(window=10, min_count=1)\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "execution_count": 13,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Computing transition probabilities: 100%|██████████| 13654/13654 [00:02<00:00, 5110.96it/s]\n"
          ],
          "name": "stderr"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "AhrtjQ66FE79",
        "colab_type": "code",
        "colab": {}
      },
      "source": [
        "player_nodes = [x for x in model.wv.vocab]\n",
        "embeddings = np.array([model.wv[x] for x in player_nodes])\n",
        "\n",
        "tsne = TSNE(n_components=2, random_state=7, perplexity=15)\n",
        "embeddings_2d = tsne.fit_transform(embeddings)"
      ],
      "execution_count": 0,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "2kpi9tRxFJrk",
        "colab_type": "code",
        "colab": {}
      },
      "source": [
        "team_colors = {}\n",
        "maximum = df['community'].max()\n",
        "for items in range(maximum+1):\n",
        "    team_colors[items] = (randint(0,255))"
      ],
      "execution_count": 0,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "DoW-1e7UFLjt",
        "colab_type": "code",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 537
        },
        "outputId": "5a3d87d6-ca38-4075-8e43-cd5532245820"
      },
      "source": [
        "df['color'] = df['community'].apply(lambda x: team_colors[x])\n",
        "player_colors = dict(zip(df['node'], df['color']))\n",
        "#print (player_colors)\n",
        "player_nodes = [ str(x) for x in player_nodes ]\n",
        "colors = [player_colors[x] for x in player_nodes]\n",
        "\n",
        "figure = plt.figure(figsize=(11, 9))\n",
        "\n",
        "ax = figure.add_subplot(111)\n",
        "\n",
        "ax.scatter(embeddings_2d[:, 0], embeddings_2d[:, 1], c=colors)\n",
        "\n",
        "figure.savefig('/content/drive/My Drive/data/HEPAuthor.png')"
      ],
